A community of Bitcoin users wishing to help the bitcoin economy by adding a better way to buy, sell and trade goods and services.

The service was announced Febrary 25th, 2011 (1.1).

##Buying
This is a Bitcoin only site at the moment with no Paypal or other service at the moment.

##Selling
There is no fee for listing.

Currently, as of Feb 23 2011 there are no fees and no advertisements.

